decimal value is 16537

than go to http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Xbox_360_system_software
go to 1.1 2.0.16537.0 download it,
1.) Unrar/zip the download
2.) Copy the $SystemUpdate folder to the root of a USB Stick (The memory stick must be FAT or Fat32 formatted)
3.) Insert the USB Stick into your Xbox 360 console.